-- TCS subsidiary gets multi-million pound deal from Friends Life Management 
-- By Nivedita Bhattacharjee in Mumbai
-- Tue Aug 19, 2014 03:25AM EDT
-- None



Aug 19 (Reuters) - Tata Consultancy Services <TCS.NS> said its subsidiary Diligenta had signed a multi-million pound deal with financial services company Friends Life Management Services Ltd for its international operations.

Under the deal, Diligenta will implement TCS BaNCS, the IT service provider's banking services platform, to support international operations of Friends Life in Asia Pacific and the Middle East, TCS said.